README
======

Documentation of an Ansible project

* Copy template from vbotka.ansible/contrib/docs

  shell> find docs -type f | xargs sed -i 's/__AUTHOR_FULL_NAME__/Vladimir Botka/g'
  shell> find docs -type f | xargs sed -i 's/__COPYRIGHT_HOLDER__/Vladimir Botka/g'
  shell> find docs -type f | xargs sed -i 's/__GITHUB_USERNAME__/vbotka/g'
  shell> find docs -type f | xargs sed -i 's/__PROJECT__/wpa_cli/g'
  shell> find docs -type f | xargs sed -i 's/ansible-wpa_cli/ansible-freebsd-wpa-cli/g'

* Update version

  shell> grep "version =" source/conf.py 
  version = '0.1'

* See annotation/README

  Create lists of files and vars
  shell> ls -1 tasks > docs/annotation/tasks-list.txt
  shell> ls -1 templates/ > docs/annotation/templates-list.txt
  shell> cd annotation; ansible-playbook pb-annotations.yml

* Create source/annotation-*.rst

  shell> ansible-playbook playbook.yml

* Create html documents

  shell> make html

* Create LaTex and PDF documents

  shell> make latexpdf

* Create epub documents

  shell> make epub

* See the documents

  shell> browser build/html/index.html

# EOF
